# College Chatbot (Rasa + HTML Frontend)

This guide explains how to set up and run the College Chatbot using **Rasa** as the backend and an HTML page as the frontend.

---

## 📦 1. Requirements
- Python 3.8–3.11 installed
- Rasa installed (`pip install rasa`)
- (Optional) Rasa SDK for actions (`pip install rasa-sdk`)
- A code editor (VS Code recommended)
- Browser to run the HTML page

---

## 🗂 2. Project Structure
project-folder/
│
├── actions/ # Custom action files (optional)
├── data/ # NLU + Stories
├── domain.yml # Rasa domain config
├── config.yml # Pipeline config
├── credentials.yml # API credentials (includes rest webhook)
├── endpoints.yml # Action server endpoints
├── index.html # Your chatbot HTML file
└── ...

yaml
